entry.title: Weight-Loss Drugs Like Ozempic Are Treating Binge Eating, Too
entry.content: Patients say weight-loss drugs have helped control their eating disorders. Some doctors are skeptical.

entry.title: Ukraine Strikes Russian Logistics, Recaptures Village
entry.content: Ukrainian forces attacked the Russian-occupied south and said they recaptured another village, showing Kyiv’s strategy of probing Russia’s front lines for weaknesses while seeking to choke supplies to the troops manning them.
